OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: 'Terrified'   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBritish Council teachers   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstill in hiding            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Afghans who were employed to spread    
OL,6, British values and teach English in    
OL,7, Helmand province have told the BBC they
OL,8, are still in hiding from the Taliban   
OL,9, and remain "terrified of reprisals".   
OL,11,FAround 100 ex-British Council staff are
OL,12,Fstill in Afghanistan having so far been
OL,13,Fdenied the right to come to the UK.    
OL,15,F"We are all sitting inside, like in    
OL,16,Fprison," one said, while another said  
OL,17,Fthey were now running out of money.    
OL,19,FThe Foreign Office said a new scheme   
OL,20,Fwill bring thousands more to the UK.   
